    <strong>Q1: Where’s the best trout pond near Hillsboro?</strong><br>
    <strong>Bethany Pond</strong> — stocked heavily in spring, family-friendly, paved paths .
</p>
<p>
    <strong>Q2: Do I need a license?</strong><br>
